PrecisORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (1998- No.5, FIRST NATION OF NACHO NYAK DUN, Y.T.) - which prohibits the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals in certain areas of the Yukon, and (b) provides for the repeal of the Prohibition Order made by Order in Council P.C. 1995-277.
